      <title>特朗普的财政部选择导致美元下跌，基本金属价格上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-25/base-metals-climb-as-dollar-drops-after-trump-s-treasury-choice</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国当选总统唐纳德·特朗普慎重挑选财政部长后，美元下跌，基本金属和铁矿石价格上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-25/base-metals-climb-as-dollar-drops-after-trump-s-treasury-choice</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 25 Nov 2024 03:13:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国诉讼案引发市场崩溃后，阿达尼寻求安抚投资者</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-25/adani-touts-sufficient-cash-after-rout-sparked-by-us-charges</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度阿达尼集团表示，其拥有足够的现金来偿还债务，此前美国对创始人高塔姆·阿达尼的贿赂起诉引发了该集团股票和债券的抛售，该集团试图安抚债权人。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-25/adani-touts-sufficient-cash-after-rout-sparked-by-us-charges</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 25 Nov 2024 02:31:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>京成电气激进投资者持股推动日本铁路股飙升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-25/japan-s-rail-stocks-soar-on-keisei-electric-activist-stake-news</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周一有报道称激进投资者村上义明 (Yoshiaki Murakami) 相关的基金已入股日本火车运营商京成电铁公司和京急电铁公司，这两家公司的股价随之上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-25/japan-s-rail-stocks-soar-on-keisei-electric-activist-stake-news</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 25 Nov 2024 01:34:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>股票、债券上涨，交易员对国债选择感到高兴：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-24/dollar-falls-as-treasury-pick-tempers-trump-bets-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亚洲股市和美国国债的强劲走势似乎将延续到欧洲，因为交易员们对唐纳德·特朗普选择斯科特·贝森特担任财政部长表示欢迎，认为这是一个深思熟虑的选择，将为美国经济和金融市场注入更多稳定性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-24/dollar-falls-as-treasury-pick-tempers-trump-bets-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 24 Nov 2024 22:39:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
